'''The Brothers Hildebrandt 2002 Calendar''' was published by Entertainment Calendar, LLC. The calendar contains illustrations by the [[Brothers Hildebrandt]] as well as photos of their posing sessions that have survived the 25 years since the first calendar was published.

* ISBN 1-58774-055-9
* Dimensions: 12 x 12 inches
* Stapled
* Punched hanging hole
* Shrink-wrapped
